	</div>
	<div id = "pharmacy">
		<ul class = "about-list">	
			<li class = "about-list-3">
				<h1>Better customer service, convenience, and loyalty</h1>
				<ul>
				<li>Pillist will offer pharmacies an innovative and differentiable clinical tool for their customers</li>
				<li>Pharmacies will be able to increase prescription volume and improve customer service with
convenient refills and better customer communication</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			
