				<h1>Physicans need:</h1>
				<p>to perform efficient Medication Reconciliations and deliver the

	best possible care while caregivers need this information to help the patient take his or her medications.</p>
			</li> -->
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div id = "physician">
		<ul class = "about-list">	
			<li class = "about-list-5">
			<h1>Accurate and updated medication lists</h1>
				<ul>
				<li>Pillist will allow physicians and other providers to have access to their patient’s organized and updated medication list to perform an efficient and accurate medication reconciliation</li>
				<li>Physicians will be able to review the patient’s refill data to differentiate between medication efficacy and medication adherence to provide better care</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
	<!-- 		<div id = "email-input">
				
					<input autocomplete = "off" id = "email" placeholder = "email address" type = "text">
